headline: Assessing AT&T’s (T) Valuation After a Quiet but Steady Climb in 2024
summary: AT&T (T) is on the minds of investors once again, with its recent moves in the market prompting a closer look at the stock’s longer-term potential. There hasn’t been a single headline-making event such as a spin-off, acquisition, or regulatory surprise, but the way AT&T has traded lately is enough to get people wondering what’s next. Whenever a steady name like AT&T makes subtle shifts, it is often a sign to step back and see if the market is rethinking its prospects or simply shuffling the...
